description:
In the rainforest we see beauty, order, design, precision and balance. This indicates that the Rainforest is the outcome of intention rather than chance.  Its the result of design rather than accident.  The Rainforest tells us as forcefully as anything can, that a Master Designer has been at work.  The Bible identifies this Master Designer in its opening sentence. Watch the program to learn more.
